parameters: Umi "Mia... collapsed when I woke up in the morning!"
Kru "Is she sick? Is this the first time this has happened?"
Umi "It's the first time... Mia is always energetic"
Kru "I'll go consult with the tribal chief!"
Kru: "Umi... I heard from the chief... You can't leave the forest?"
Umi: "Umi feels like she has to do something about it."

Kru: "Despite facing such a tough situation, you're trying to persevere and
overcome it."

Umi: "Umi is weak... But the reason she thinks about becoming stronger is
because of Mia..."

Umi: "Yes. Ever since Toto and Kaka disappeared, Umi became unable to
speak... It was very troubling..."

Umi: "At that time, Umi met Mia in the forest. Mia was just a kitten
and very weak, and Umi thought she had to do something about it. After
that, somehow strength welled up inside her..."

Umi: "And then Umi became able to speak again... She got better in order to
raise Mia."
Kru: "I see... So the Umi we have now is thanks to Mia, huh?"

Umi: "That's right... If it weren't for Mia, Umi would have remained sad
forever. She's still sad, but now there are other feelings too..."

Umi: "Like being happy with Mia, or enjoying delicious meat, and also
with you..."

Umi: "Mmm... It's nothing. Anyway... I'm scared, but I'll go get that
herb."
Umi: "If I'm with you... I feel like I can do my best."
Kru: "Everything will be fine for sure! I'm with you! Let's go!"
Umi "Kru! Welcome back. Did you finish talking with the chief?"

Kru "Yeah, it's over. The chief wants to open up the village and interact
with the kingdom. I've been chosen as the envoy."
Umi "Kru is busy. The chief is working you too hard."
Kru "That's okay, but... Umi, you've been chosen as an envoy too."
Kru "The chief wants to talk to us about it, so shall we go together?"
Kru "Umi... It's okay, I'm with you."
Kru "Besides, we've overcome so many things up to now, it'll be fine."
Umi "Hic, sob...sob sob...waaaah!! I'm so happy..."
Umi "Kru... thank you. For taking me with you..."
Kru "No, it's nothing big. I'm just really glad Mia is safe..."

Umi "Sob... right. I wonder if everyone in the village is okay? Kru, could
you go check for me?"
Umi: "How was everyone in the village?"
